snippet.title: Super Smash Kart 64 Demo V1 RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Super Smash Kart is a mod of Mario Kart 64 I've been working on for a while now, and I'm glad to have finally been able to release the first demo of the mod. It features four new courses and four new characters. I hope you enjoy playing it.

Download the mod here: https://mega.nz/file/QSoizQxC#o3bYy-uQEJyU5-SlWwywGRXzMzXq6IN5pFmaLv3WoC4

Huge thanks to everyone that helped me in the Overkart 64 Discord server: https://discord.gg/WEn7vBuE

Join my Discord server: https://discord.gg/Sz3pYSwdm4
